<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<tools>
	<tool name="PDA">
		<title><![CDATA[Smartphone]]></title>
		<text><![CDATA[You've acquired a smartphone
Check out these great features:
<li>Messages - Instant communications!</li>
<li>Clues - Records every clue you find.</li>
<li>Evidence - Records all the evidence you find by locations.</li>]]></text>
	</tool>
	<tool name="Swabs">
		<title><![CDATA[Swabs]]></title>
		<text><![CDATA[You’ve acquired some swabs
These swabs can be used to collect cheek cells from persons of interest for DNA analysis. 
To use these swabs, click them and then click a person of interest.
]]></text>
	</tool>
	<tool name="Camera">
		<title><![CDATA[Camera]]></title>
		<text><![CDATA[You’ve acquired a camera
Photos from the crime scene can be used to determine the position of the body at the time of shooting.
To use this camera, click it and then click an object at the crime scene.]]></text>
	</tool>
</tools>